docs/ (Human Guides)

Plain-language guides for humans of all backgrounds — not just techies. Some ideas:

guides/for-developers.md – How to integrate covenant principles into AI design, ML pipelines, data practices.

guides/for-organizations.md – Sample policies, ethical review checklists, governance templates.

guides/for-educators.md – Lesson plans, classroom discussion prompts, activities.

guides/for-communities.md – How to host a local covenant workshop or conversation circle.
